videos.description: Devon Hall knocks down his second 3-pointer for the Cavaliers.
videos.headline: Hall gets Virginia going with quick 3

videos.description: Jack Salt collects the deflected pass on the run and slams it home for Virginia.
videos.headline: Salt follows with big dunk

videos.description: Justin Bibbs pulls up for a 3-pointer as the Hokies jump out to a 22-13 lead over the Cavaliers.
videos.headline: VT caps off 17-0 run with 3 ball

videos.description: De'Andre Hunter gets the ball in the paint and draws the foul to get the Cavs back in the game.
videos.headline: UVA's Hunter extends for the and-1

videos.description: Justin Robinson fires a rocket to Nickeil Alexander-Walker as he gets a 3-pointer off before the buzzer to put the Hokies up 33-26.
videos.headline: VT hits buzzer-beater 3 at the half

videos.description: Virginia Tech head coach Buzz Williams says in order for his team to keep its pace they have match attempted field goals with the Cavaliers as the Hokies enter the half with a 33-26 lead.
videos.headline: Williams: 'We have to shoot as much as they do'

videos.description: Devon Hall hits a 3-pointer as Virginia goes a on a quick 9-0 run to tie it at 35 in the second half.
videos.headline: Hall ties it for UVA with 3

videos.description: Mamadi Diakite is rewarded in the paint after a nice passing sequence from Virginia with a dunk.
videos.headline: Pretty passing leads to Diakite dunk

videos.description: Kerry Blackshear Jr. finds Devin Wilson with the backdoor pass to give the Hokies a 4-point lead with over a minute to play.
videos.headline: Wilson scores on easy backdoor for VT

videos.description: Ty Jerome finds space for the Cavaliers to tie it at 49.
videos.headline: Jerome sends it to OT for UVA

videos.description: Justin Bibbs hits a corner 3-pointer to tie the game at 54-54 in overtime for Virginia Tech.
videos.headline: Bibbs ties it for VT with a 3

videos.description: Devon Hall hits his fifth 3-pointer of the game for the Cavaliers to give his team a 3-point lead.
videos.headline: Hall answers with 3 in OT

videos.description: Kerry Blackshear Jr. follows up the missed layup from Justin Robinson with and-1 putback with seconds remaining in overtime to take down Virginia.
videos.headline: Blackshear sinks game winner in OT

videos.description: Justin Robinson says the upset win over No. 2 Virginia was huge for his team as they get deeper into ACC play.
videos.headline: VT's Robinson: 'This road win was huge'
